# Architecture

**Phase 1:** `auth` schema only — ignore `exam` and `better-s3`.

**Dependency:** sub-feature → segment `lib/` → `src/lib` | `src/components`. No cross-sibling imports (e.g. `members/` → not `teams/`).

**Colocate:** pages, UI, feature `lib/`, actions at `src/app/action/<feature>/` (one mutation per file).

**Single source of truth:** `*-routes.ts` and `cache-tags.ts` per segment; badges in shared config; UI from `src/components/ui`. Base UI links: `render={<Link … />}`, not `asChild`.

Before new helpers: pick scope upward; compose shadcn primitives first; stay minimal.

